comments.body:
@matpen My confusion with this one is I remember reviewing the code a few weeks back, but the PR (https://github.com/containers/libpod/pull/3617) was just merged a few days ago.  This functionality is only currently available in upstream Podman and will be part of the next release.  You can verify this by doing `man podman run` and I'm sure you won't see the `--pull` option there.  The online man page is valid for the upstream version of Podman only.

If you can build Podman from GitHub, then the --pull will be available.

Hope that helps!  I'm going to close this issue.
